---
<footer class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-400 py-20 border-t-2 border-blue-600/30 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Glowing gradient accent overlay -->
  <div class="absolute left-[-10%] top-0 w-[450px] h-[450px] bg-blue-600/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute right-[-10%] bottom-0 w-[450px] h-[450px] bg-teal-600/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <!-- Main Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 pb-16 border-b border-slate-800">
      
      <!-- Column 1: Brand Info (4 cols width) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6">
        <a href="#" class="flex items-center gap-2 group w-fit">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-tr from-blue-600 to-blue-400 flex items-center justify-center font-display font-black text-white text-lg tracking-wider shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/10 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform">
            V
          </div>
          <span class="font-display font-black text-lg tracking-widest text-white group-hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors">VORTEXA</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          Kami merancang antarmuka web interaktif berkinerja tinggi (Frontend-only), visualisasi data waktu nyata, dan sistem agen AI otomatis untuk membantu bisnis Anda tumbuh tanpa kerumitan server database.
        </p>
        
